high_descs: Turn around and walk into the opposite room, then turn right by facing the desk.
Pick the mug from the table.
Turn right and head to the microwave on the kitchen counter by turning right.
Place the mug in the oven and heat it, then take the mug out.
Place the mug in the left most upper cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Place the Mug in the Cabinet by heating it.

high_descs: Turn around and walk around the bed, exiting the doorway near the foot of the bed, then go straight ahead to the next room and to the first desk on the right.
Pick up the mug from the desk.
Exit the room you came in, turn right and go until reaching the kitchen area, heading right again towards the microwave.
Use the microwave on the mug then remove the mug.
Look up to the upper cabinet to the right of the microwave, in the corner of the room.
Put the mug in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Heat a mug in a microwave and place it in a kitchen cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the desk.
Take the mug from the desk.
Turn around and go near the microwave.
Put the mug into the microwave.
Then take it out and go near the cabinet.
Put the mug into the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Placed the mug into the cabinet.
